* Web API design tips

- Don't be clever
- Be boring and obvious
- Impress with functionality
- Talk JSON
- RESTful over HTTP
- Status codes (200 == OK, 404 == Not Found)
- Version it
  GET /api/v1/wonderful-things/
- SSL (HTTPS) every time (check out Cloudflare.com)
- Make output pretty (human readable)
- Use the web (caching)

